rows.label: tlk79000007_04_msg0002
rows.name: I know you'll come back! You have to!

rows.label: tlk79000007_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Don't worry about us Sata and
I'll be waiting right here!

rows.label: tlk79000007_04_msg0101
rows.name:
I wish I were stronger, like
Adel-sama and the rest of you.

rows.label: tlk79000007_04_msg0102
rows.name:
When all this is over, and
you come back for us...

rows.label: tlk79000007_04_msg0103
rows.name:
Well, maybe Sata will
finally show you a smile

rows.label: tlk79000007_04_msg0104
rows.name:
I doubt he actually will,
but, eh, I'll try my best!
